	dprr:hasNoteText "Monetalis. In MRR 2.454, and Index, 630, refer also to Crawford, RRC 1.457, no. 435, 53 B.C. He was perhaps the cos. suff. of 32 (no. 255), or a son of the cos. of 53 (268).\n" .
